@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="Environment Audit Designated Agency (EADA) - Precise Reference Branding" />
    <title>EADA | Environment Audit Designated Agency</title>

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400..900;1,400..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        :root {
            --forest-green: #0b6623;
            --forest-green-dark: #005a2b;
            --accent-yellow: #f59e0b;
            --text-dark: #1f2937;
            --text-muted: #6b7280;
            --border-color: #e5e7eb;
            --container-w: 1280px;
            --hero-bg: #4b4b4b; /* Charcoal from reference */
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: var(--text-dark); background: #fdfdfd; line-height: 1.5; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        h1, h2, h3, .serif { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
        
        .container { max-width: var(--container-w); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }
        .flex-between { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }

        /* --- 1. Top Government Identity (Slim White/Light Strip) --- */
        .gov-strip {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding: 0.3rem 0;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .gov-strip-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .gov-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
        .flag-box { width: 18px; height: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: linear-gradient(#FF9933 33.3%, #ffffff 33.3% 66.6%, #128807 66.6%); }

        /* --- 2. White Logo / Branding Strip --- */
        .branding-strip {
            padding: 1rem 0;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .branding-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        
        .brand-logos-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
        .logo-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem; }
        .brand-titles { text-align: left; margin-left: 0.5rem; }
        .brand-titles h1 { font-size: 1.85rem; font-weight: 900; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
        .brand-titles p { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 4px; }

        .brand-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
        
        .badge-logo, .mini-logo { 
            position: relative; background: transparent; border: none; box-shadow: none;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; text-align: center;
        }
        .mini-logo { width: 52px; height: 52px; overflow: hidden; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .badge-logo { height: 42px; min-width: 65px; flex-shrink: 0; }

        .badge-logo:not(:last-child)::after {
            content: ''; position: absolute;
            right: -0.75rem; /* Centers the line in the 1.5rem gap */
            top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%);
            height: 75%; width: 1px;
            background-color: #cbd5e1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        
        .badge-logo img, .mini-logo img { 
            max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain; z-index: 2; position: relative; box-shadow: none; filter: none; border: none;
        }
        
        .logo-fallback { 
            position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 800; color: #94a3b8; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center;
            padding: 2px; line-height: 1.1; z-index: 1; margin: 0;
        }
        
        /* Language/Accessibility Dropdown like reference Blue */
        .util-dropdown {
            background: #004a99; color: white; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; cursor: pointer;
        }

        /* --- 3. Green Navigation Bar --- */
        .navbar-wrap { background: var(--forest-green-dark); }
        .nav-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; height: 52px; }
        
        .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center; }
        .nav-link { 
            text-decoration: none; color: #ffffff; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; 
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 5px; opacity: 0.95; transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .nav-link:hover { opacity: 1; }
        .nav-link i { font-size: 1rem; }

        /* Dropdown Styles */
        .nav-item-dropdown { position: relative; }
        .dropdown-menu {
            display: none; position: absolute; top: 100%; left: 0;
            background: #ffffff; min-width: 280px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 0.5rem 0; z-index: 100;
        }
        .nav-item-dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu { display: block; }
        .dropdown-item {
            display: block; padding: 0.75rem 1.25rem; color: #1f2937;
            text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.2s; border-left: 3px solid transparent; text-align: left;
        }
        .dropdown-item:hover {
            background: #f0fdf4; color: var(--forest-green-dark);
            border-left: 3px solid var(--forest-green-dark);
        }

        /* --- 4. Scrolling Notice Strip --- */
        .notice-strip { display: flex; align-items: center; background: #e0f2fe; border-bottom: 1px solid #bae6fd; font-size: 0.85rem; height: 38px; overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
        .notice-badge { background: #0284c7; color: white; padding: 0 1.25rem; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; z-index: 2; position: relative; }
        .notice-badge::after { content:''; position: absolute; right: -10px; top:0; width:0; height:0; border-top: 19px solid transparent; border-bottom: 19px solid transparent; border-left: 10px solid #0284c7; }
        .marquee-container { flex: 1; overflow: hidden; position: relative; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; }
        .marquee-text { white-space: nowrap; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; animation: marquee 25s linear infinite; padding-left: 100%; }
        @@keyframes marquee {
            from { transform: translateX(0); }
            to { transform: translateX(-100%); }
        }

        /* --- 5. Hero Section (PARIVESH Style) --- */
        .hero {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 55% 45%;
            min-height: 520px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .hero-left {
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #f1f5f9;
        }

        /* Carousel/Slider Infrastructure */
        .hero-slider {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
        }

        .hero-slide {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            z-index: 1;
        }
        .hero-slide.active { opacity: 1; z-index: 2; }

        .slide-overlay {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,0.15), transparent);
            z-index: 3;
        }

        /* Slider Nav Arrows */
        .slider-nav {
            position: absolute; top: 50%; width: 100%;
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 1.5rem; transform: translateY(-50%);
            z-index: 10; pointer-events: none;
        }
        .nav-btn {
            width: 44px; height: 44px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px); border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: white; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            cursor: pointer; pointer-events: auto; transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); transform: scale(1.1); }

        /* Slider Dots */
        .slider-pagination {
            position: absolute; bottom: 2rem; left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%); display: flex; gap: 0.6rem;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .pag-dot {
            width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); cursor: pointer; transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .pag-dot.active { background: #ffffff; width: 30px; border-radius: 10px; }

        .hero-right {
            background: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 3rem;
        }

        .eada-logo-minimal {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .eada-logo-minimal img {
            width: 280px;
            height: auto;
            max-width: 90%;
            object-fit: contain;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05));
        }


        /* --- Footer & Cards (Maintained) --- */
        .modules-section { padding: 5rem 0; background: #f8fafc; }
        .mod-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
        .mod-card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 3rem; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; transition: 0.3s; }
        .mod-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }

        /* --- 7. About Section --- */
        .about-section { padding: 4rem 0 5rem; background: #ffffff; }
        .about-card {
            background: #ffffff; padding: 3.5rem 4rem; border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03); 
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .about-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
        .about-content p {
            color: #374151; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: justify;
        }
        .about-content p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        footer { background: #012a14; color: white; padding: 5rem 0 3rem; }

        /* --- Responsiveness --- */
        @@media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-left { padding-top: 5rem; padding-bottom: 5rem; }
            .hero-left { min-height: 300px; }
            .eada-logo-minimal img { width: 220px; }
            .branding-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center; }
            .brand-logos-left { justify-content: center; }
            .brand-right { justify-content: center; gap: 1rem; }
            .badge-logo:not(:last-child)::after { display: none; }
            .nav-inner { flex-direction: column; height: auto; padding: 1rem 0; gap: 1rem; }
            
            .nav-item-dropdown:hover .dropdown-menu { position: static; display: block; box-shadow: none; border: none; padding-left: 1rem; width: 100%; background: transparent; }
            .dropdown-item { color: #f8fafc; }
            .dropdown-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: white; border-color: transparent; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- 1. Top Government Identity Strip -->
    <div class="gov-strip">
        <div class="container gov-strip-inner">
            <div class="gov-left">
                <div class="flag-box"></div>
                <span>भारत सरकार | Government of India</span>
            </div>
            <div class="brand-right" style="gap: 1rem;">
                <span style="border-right: 1px solid #ccc; padding-right: 10px;">A- A A+</span>
                <div class="util-dropdown">EN ▾</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 2. White Logo / Branding Strip -->
    <div class="branding-strip">
        <div class="container branding-inner">
            <div class="brand-logos-left">
                <div class="logo-group">
                    <div class="mini-logo">
                        <img src="/images/branding/logo_emblem.png" alt="Emblem" onerror="this.style.opacity='0'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
                        <span class="logo-fallback" style="display:none;">Emblem</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mini-logo">
                        <img src="/images/branding/logo_eada.png" alt="EADA" onerror="this.style.opacity='0'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
                        <span class="logo-fallback" style="display:none;">EADA Logo</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="brand-titles">
                    <h1>EADA</h1>
                    <p>Environment Audit Designated Agency</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="brand-right">
                <div class="badge-logo">
                    <img src="/images/branding/logo_azadi.png" alt="Azadi" onerror="this.style.opacity='0'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
                    <span class="logo-fallback" style="display:none;">Azadi 75</span>
                </div>
                <div class="badge-logo">
                    <img src="/images/branding/logo_life.png" alt="LiFE" onerror="this.style.opacity='0'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
                    <span class="logo-fallback" style="display:none;">LiFE</span>
                </div>
                <a href="https://www.npcindia.gov.in/NPC/User/index" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="badge-logo">
                    <img src="/images/branding/logo_npc.png" alt="NPC" onerror="this.style.opacity='0'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex';" />
                    <span class="logo-fallback" style="display:none;">NPC</span>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. Forest Green Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="navbar-wrap">
        <div class="container nav-inner">
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">About EADA</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://static.pib.gov.in/WriteReadData/specificdocs/documents/2025/sep/doc202593627401.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="nav-link">Rules</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item-dropdown">
                    <a href="#" class="nav-link">Guidelines ▾</a>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu">
                        <a href="~/docs/guideline for cea through rpl.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="dropdown-item">Guideline for CEA through RPL</a>
                        <a href="~/docs/guideline for rea.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="dropdown-item">Guideline for REA</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- 4. Scrolling Notice Strip -->
    <div class="notice-strip">
        <div class="notice-badge">Latest Update</div>
        <div class="marquee-container">
            <div class="marquee-text">
                The Environment Audit Designated Agency (EADA) under the Environment Audit Rules, 2025 is now live. | Apply for EC/FC/WL/CRZ via the official portal framework.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 5. Hero Section (PARIVESH Style) -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-left">
            <div class="hero-slider">
                <!-- Slide 1 -->
                <div class="hero-slide active" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542601906990-b4d3fb778b09?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=600');">
                    <div class="slide-overlay"></div>
                </div>
                
                <!-- Navigation UI -->
                <div class="slider-nav">
                    <div class="nav-btn prev">❮</div>
                    <div class="nav-btn next">❯</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Pagination UI -->
                <div class="slider-pagination">
                    <div class="pag-dot active"></div>
                    <div class="pag-dot"></div>
                    <div class="pag-dot"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="hero-right">
            <div class="eada-logo-minimal">
                <img src="/images/branding/logo_eada.png" alt="EADA Official Logo" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/400x400/ffffff/065f46.png?text=EADA'" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. Modules Section -->
    <section class="modules-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="mod-grid">
                <article class="mod-card">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--forest-green-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Recognition of Prior Learning (CEA RPL)</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">A dedicated portal for existing environmental professionals to certify their expertise and align with the EADA framework.</p>
                    <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; background: #fffbeb; color: #92400e; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.8rem;">⏳ Coming Soon</span>
                </article>

                <article class="mod-card">
                    <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--forest-green-dark); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Registered Environmental Auditor (REA)</h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Official registry and auditing management system for environmental compliance monitoring across industrial sectors.</p>
                    <span style="display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; background: #f0fdf4; color: #166534; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.8rem;">⏳ Coming Soon</span>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. About Section -->
    <section class="about-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-card">
                <div class="about-icon">🏛️</div>
                <h2 class="serif" style="color: var(--forest-green-dark); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 2.2rem; text-align: center;">About Environment Audit Designated Agency (EADA)</h2>
                <div class="about-content">
                    <p>The Environment Audit Designated Agency (EADA) is a role established under the Environment Audit Rules, 2025, notified by the Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change (MoEF&CC) on 29 August 2025. The EADA is responsible for the overall management of the environmental audit framework in India.</p>
                    <p>The framework is designed to strengthen compliance with major environmental legislations, including the Environment (Protection) Act, 1986; Water (Prevention and Control of Pollution) Act, 1974; Air (Prevention and Control of Pollution) Act, 1981; Van (Sanrakshan Evam Samvardhan) Adhiniyam, 1980; the Wild Life (Protection) Act, 1972; and rules framed thereunder. It also supports compliance with regulatory approvals such as Environmental Clearance (EC), Consent to Establish (CTE), and Consent to Operate (CTO).</p>
                    <p>The EADA's key responsibilities include specifying eligibility criteria for Certified Environmental Auditors (CEA) and Registered Environmental Auditors (REA), developing certification and screening methodologies, managing auditor registration, renewal, suspension and cancellation, monitoring auditor performance, issuing directions, taking disciplinary action, facilitating capacity building through training programmes and workshops, specifying guidelines and standards for auditors, and maintaining a publicly accessible online register of all certified and registered auditors.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 4rem;">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="serif" style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">EADA Portal</h3>
                    <p style="opacity: 0.7; max-width: 500px; font-size: 0.95rem;">Empowered oversight for a sustainable nation. EADA is an initiative of the Ministry of Environment, Forest and Climate Change, Government of India.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: right;">
                    <h4 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Support</h4>
                    <p style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem;">helpdesk&#64;eada.gov.in</p>
                    <p style="opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">+91 11 2345 6789</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.5; text-align: center;">
                &copy; 2026 Environment Audit Designated Agency. All Rights Reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>